script.name: plugin.guilds.loadconfig
script.sourceplaintext:
* Setup config $guild.config = get global variable: name='guilds.config'
* dynamic config values are changable in game, dont override these $dynamic = table alloc $dynamic['seta.resume'] = [TRUE] $dynamic['seta.sensitivity'] = [TRUE] $dynamic['gate.safety'] = [TRUE] $dynamic['marines.add'] = [TRUE] $dynamic['khaak.jobs'] = [TRUE] $dynamic['xenon.jobs'] = [TRUE] $dynamic['sector.colours'] = [TRUE]
* static configs shoul only change on first load $static = table alloc $static['max.prosperity'] = [TRUE]
if $a.force OR ! $guild.config $config = table alloc gosub sub.LoadConfig gosub sub.ApplySettings set global variable: name='guilds.config' value=$config else $config = $guild.config gosub sub.LoadConfig $version = $settings['settings.version'] $config.version = $config['settings.version'] if $version > $config.version gosub sub.ApplySettings $config['settings.version'] = $version end end
return null
sub.LoadConfig: gosub sub.DefaultConfig
$file = read types file lines: filename='TGuilds' if $file $file = combine string array: $file, separator=' ' $XML.Data = parse xml data: $file if $XML.Data $xml.node = xml get node string: $XML.Data if $xml.node == 'Guilds' $settings.node = xml find child: $XML.Data, node='settings' if $settings.node $xml.attr = xml get attribute: data=$settings.node, attribute='version' do if $xml.attr $settings['settings.version'] = $xml.attr
$xml.lookup = table alloc $arr = create new array, arguments='off', 'current', 'yours', 'all', null $xml.lookup['gate.safety'] = $arr $arr = create new array, arguments='few', 'some', 'half', 'lots', 'all' $xml.lookup['marines.add'] = $arr
$xml.table = table alloc $xml.table.data = table alloc $xml.table['bbs'] = $xml.table.data $xml.table.data['min'] = 'bbs.min' $xml.table.data['max'] = 'bbs.max' $xml.table.data['mindynamic'] = 'bbs.min.dynamic' $xml.table.data['dock'] = 'bbs.dock' $xml.table.data = table alloc $xml.table['jobs'] = $xml.table.data $xml.table.data['xenon'] = 'xenon.jobs' $xml.table.data['khaak'] = 'khaak.jobs' $xml.table.data = table alloc $xml.table['economy'] = $xml.table.data $xml.table.data['positive'] = 'econ.sector.pos' $xml.table.data['negative'] = 'econ.sector.neg' $xml.table.data = table alloc $xml.table['merchant'] = $xml.table.data $xml.table.data['sats'] = 'merchant.sats' $xml.table.data = table alloc $xml.table['planetary'] = $xml.table.data $xml.table.data['maxprosperity'] = 'max.prosperity' $xml.table.data = table alloc $xml.table['bounty'] = $xml.table.data $xml.table.data['max'] = 'max.bounty' $xml.table.data['race'] = 'max.bounty.race' $xml.table.data['range'] = 'bounty.range' $xml.table.data = table alloc $xml.table['passenger'] = $xml.table.data $xml.table.data['wait'] = 'passenger.create.wait' $xml.table.data['sector'] = 'max.passenger.sector' $xml.table.data['range'] = 'passenger.board.range' $xml.table.data = table alloc $xml.table['guilds'] = $xml.table.data $xml.table.data['hqrespawn'] = 'hq.respawn' $xml.table.data['board.dock'] = 'guildboard.dock' $xml.table.data = table alloc $xml.table['seta'] = $xml.table.data $xml.table.data['resume'] = 'seta.resume' $xml.table.data['sensitivity'] = 'seta.sensitivity' $xml.table.data = table alloc $xml.table['gatesafe'] = $xml.table.data $xml.table.data['value'] = 'gate.safety' $xml.table.data = table alloc $xml.table['marines'] = $xml.table.data $xml.table.data['add'] = 'marines.add'
$xml.count = xml get number of children: $settings.node while $xml.count dec $xml.count = $xml.node = xml get child: $settings.node, id=$xml.count $xml.name = xml get node string: $xml.node
$xml.table.data = $xml.table[$xml.name] if $xml.table.data $xml.key = get next key: table=$xml.table.data key=null while $xml.key $xml.attr = xml get attribute: data=$xml.node, attribute=$xml.key $xml.setting = $xml.table.data[$xml.key] if $xml.lookup[$xml.setting] if is datatype[ $xml.attr ] == DATATYPE_INT $settings[$xml.setting] = $xml.attr else $arr = $xml.lookup[$xml.setting] $idx = get index of $xml.attr in array $arr offset=-1 + 1 if $idx > -1 $settings[$xml.setting] = $idx end end else $settings[$xml.setting] = $xml.attr end $xml.key = get next key: table=$xml.table.data key=$xml.key end end end end $colours.node = xml find child: $XML.Data, node='colours' if $colours.node $xml.table = table alloc $xml.table['argon'] = Argon $xml.table['boron'] = Boron $xml.table['split'] = Split $xml.table['paranid'] = Paranid $xml.table['teladi'] = Teladi $xml.table['player'] = Player $xml.table['xenon'] = Xenon $xml.table['khaak'] = Kha'ak $xml.table['pirate'] = Pirates $xml.table['goner'] = Goner $xml.table['neutral'] = Neutral Race $xml.table['contested'] = Enemy Race $xml.table['guilds'] = Guilds $xml.table['other'] = Other $xml.table['privateer'] = Privateer $xml.table['atf'] = ATF $xml.table['terran'] = Terran $xml.table['yaki'] = Yaki $xml.table['otas'] = OTAS $xml.table['terracorp'] = TerraCorp $xml.table['atreus'] = Atreus $xml.table['nmmc'] = NMMC $xml.table['strongarm'] = Strong Arms $xml.table['beryll'] = Beryll $xml.table['dukes'] = Duke's $xml.table['darkspace'] = Darkspace $xml.table['industritech'] = Industritech $xml.table['pioneer'] = Pioneer
$xml.attr = xml get attribute: data=$colours.node, attribute='type' if $xml.attr == 'extended' $settings['sector.colours'] = 2 else if $xml.attr == 'basic' $settings['sector.colours'] = 1 else if $xml.attr == 'off' $settings['sector.colours'] = 0 else if is datatype[ $xml.attr ] == DATATYPE_INT $settings['sector.colours'] = $xml.attr end $xml.count = xml get number of children: $colours.node while $xml.count dec $xml.count = $xml.node = xml get child: $colours.node, id=$xml.count $xml.name = xml get node string: $xml.node if $xml.name == 'race' $xml.attr = xml get attribute: data=$xml.node, attribute='id' $xml.race = null if is datatype[ $xml.attr ] == DATATYPE_INT $xml.race = $xml.attr else $xml.race = $xml.table[$xml.attr] do if $xml.race $xml.race = get race id for race: $xml.race end if $xml.race $xml.child.type = 'captial' gosub sub.XMLDoColour $xml.child.type = 'core' gosub sub.XMLDoColour $xml.child.type = 'border' gosub sub.XMLDoColour end end end end end end end
if $settings['khaak.jobs'] set plot flag: 16384, on=[TRUE] else set plot flag: 16384, on=[FALSE] end if $settings['xenon.jobs'] activate job: id=12110 activate job: id=12111 else deactivate job: id=12110 deactivate job: id=12111 end endsub
sub.XMLDoColour: $xml.child = xml find child: $xml.node, node=$xml.child.type if $xml.child $xml.red = xml get attribute: data=$xml.child, attribute='red' skip if $xml.red $xml.red = 0 $xml.green = xml get attribute: data=$xml.child, attribute='green' skip if $xml.green $xml.green = 0 $xml.blue = xml get attribute: data=$xml.child, attribute='blue' skip if $xml.blue $xml.blue = 0 $xml.var = sprintf: fmt='sec_col.%s.%s', $xml.race, $xml.child.type, null, null, null $colour = get colour code: red=$xml.red green=$xml.green blue=$xml.blue transparency=0 $settings[$xml.var] = $colour end endsub
sub.DefaultConfig: $settings = table alloc $settings['settings.version'] = 1 $settings['econ.sector.neg'] = 3 $settings['econ.sector.pos'] = 3 $settings['merchant.sats'] = 8 $settings['bbs.min'] = 3 $settings['bbs.max'] = 5 $settings['bbs.min.dynamic'] = 1 $settings['max.prosperity'] = 10 $settings['max.bounty.race'] = 30 $settings['max.bounty'] = 100 $settings['max.passenger.sector'] = 8 $settings['passenger.create.wait'] = 120 $settings['hq.respawn'] = 20 $settings['gate.safety'] = 1 $settings['bounty.range'] = 8 $settings['seta.resume'] = [TRUE] $settings['guildboard.dock'] = [TRUE] $settings['bbs.dock'] = [TRUE] $settings['seta.sensitivity'] = 4 $settings['passenger.board.range'] = 5 $settings['marines.add'] = 3 $settings['sector.colours'] = 2 $settings['xenon.jobs'] = [TRUE] $settings['khaak.jobs'] = [TRUE] $colour = get colour code: red=170 green=255 blue=0 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.2.captial'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=15 green=255 blue=80 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.2.core'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=76 green=187 blue=23 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.2.border'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=0 green=191 blue=255 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.1.border'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=30 green=144 blue=255 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.1.core'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=0 green=0 blue=255 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.1.captial'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=165 green=0 blue=165 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.3.border'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=120 green=0 blue=120 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.3.core'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=75 green=0 blue=130 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.3.captial'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=255 green=20 blue=147 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.4.captial'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=255 green=105 blue=180 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.4.core'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=255 green=192 blue=203 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.4.border'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=255 green=255 blue=0 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.5.captial'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=255 green=255 blue=153 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.5.core'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=255 green=255 blue=204 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.5.border'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=100 green=50 blue=50 transparency=0 *$colour = get colour code: red=255 green=150 blue=0 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.6.captial'] = $colour $settings['sec_col.6.core'] = $colour $settings['sec_col.6.border'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=255 green=0 blue=255 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.7.captial'] = $colour $settings['sec_col.7.core'] = $colour $settings['sec_col.7.border'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=255 green=0 blue=0 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.8.captial'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=220 green=20 blue=60 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.8.core'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=180 green=34 blue=34 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.8.border'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=255 green=215 blue=0 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.9.captial'] = $colour $settings['sec_col.9.core'] = $colour $settings['sec_col.9.border'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=255 green=255 blue=255 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.10.captial'] = $colour $settings['sec_col.10.core'] = $colour $settings['sec_col.10.border'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=150 green=150 blue=150 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.14.captial'] = $colour $settings['sec_col.14.core'] = $colour $settings['sec_col.14.border'] = $colour *$colour = get colour code: red=128 green=0 blue=0 transparency=0 $colour = get colour code: red=250 green=250 blue=250 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.12.captial'] = $colour $settings['sec_col.12.core'] = $colour $settings['sec_col.12.border'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=0 green=255 blue=255 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.18.captial'] = $colour $settings['sec_col.17.captial'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=64 green=224 blue=208 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.17.core'] = $colour $settings['sec_col.18.core'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=0 green=206 blue=209 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.17.border'] = $colour $settings['sec_col.18.border'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=194 green=178 blue=128 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.19.captial'] = $colour $settings['sec_col.19.core'] = $colour $settings['sec_col.19.border'] = $colour
$colour = get colour code: red=194 green=252 blue=3 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.13.captial'] = $colour $settings['sec_col.13.core'] = $colour $settings['sec_col.13.border'] = $colour $colour = get colour code: red=170 green=152 blue=169 transparency=0 $colour = get colour code: red=230 green=230 blue=250 transparency=0 $settings['sec_col.15.captial'] = $colour $settings['sec_col.15.core'] = $colour $settings['sec_col.15.border'] = $colour
$colour = get colour code: red=3 green=252 blue=198 transparency=0 $i = 20 while $i <= 28 $var = sprintf: fmt='sec_col.%s.captial', $i, null, null, null, null $settings[$var] = $colour $var = sprintf: fmt='sec_col.%s.core', $i, null, null, null, null $settings[$var] = $colour $var = sprintf: fmt='sec_col.%s.border', $i, null, null, null, null $settings[$var] = $colour inc $i = end endsub
sub.ApplySettings: $key = get next key: table=$settings key=null while $key if $dynamic[$key] if not $config[$key] $config[$key] = $settings[$key] end else if $static[$key] if not $config[$key] $config[$key] = $settings[$key] end else $config[$key] = $settings[$key] end
$key = get next key: table=$settings key=$key end @ START [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.sectors : Object=null Event='reinit' Param=null Param2=null endsub return null
